{"tid":737623,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"咪再嚇人啦！卡利奧斯季前賽又派膠","createTime":"2018-07-11T03:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T07:28:07.000Z","uid":1121,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1eed6cffff3555d164c0d411ee10964b3e36a61a","tid":737623,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:30:56.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=gvI0%2BlcAl1%2BK8K%2Bnf0wR76WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=3e68991c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】利物浦門將卡利奧斯剛在季前賽3:2擊敗燦美爾又派膠，接波甩手被對方射入。<br />\n<br />\n利物浦門將卡利奧斯（Loris Karius）上屆歐聯決賽對皇家馬德里一再犯錯，全世界都看他能否重新振作。日前季前備戰接波失手，皮球滾入網中；周二季前賽3:2擊敗燦美爾時，這位德國門將又犯錯。當利物浦領先3:0時，卡利奧斯才後備入替，結果對手主射罰球，射門角度正中，他竟然一接甩手，皮球彈出被對方球員快一步射入，之後再失1球，領先3:0變險勝3:2完場。<br />\n<br />\n對於卡利奧斯再度出現低級錯誤，領隊高普說：「沒人想那樣失波，如果要追究責任的話，第2個失波就是占士米拿的錯。兩個如此出色的球員，都犯下同樣的失誤，但大家僅討論其中一人。不要每次犯錯都大造文章，一起向前看！從錯誤中學習吧！」<br />\n<br />\n高普卻承認除非卡利奧斯打幾場精彩的比賽，否則質疑之聲不會停息，稱自己的工作就是支持卡利奧斯。<br />\n<br />\n相關片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b0Vgc1AFSJ0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Db0Vgc1AFSJ0&d=gvI0%2BlcAl1%2BK8K%2Bnf0wR76WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=c459cc9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b0Vgc1AFSJ0</a>"},{"pid":"94407a42d37582b2d7cac81f7fcb21ae4620ee09","tid":737623,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5092b4e51a7a9856702b4c9a5ab47c340736110e","tid":737623,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:35:45.000Z","msg":"下季佢正選？"},{"pid":"15ff69b6d9232d0d801aa6cd1680a01032689bc5","tid":737623,"uid":44674,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:37:08.000Z","msg":"最衰都係拉莫斯"},{"pid":"ecf353b203681c759c4a246511b37cc4a0d76b07","tid":737623,"uid":52571,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:37:37.000Z","msg":"腦震盪未好返姐 笑乜閪"},{"pid":"1f6549bc4e81828b9a07e590a0c5ae9a74c36355","tid":737623,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:38:31.000Z","msg":"第二球失球做乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  利style"},{"pid":"c1a09740222ef6bc9041892983eb79a1d23733bf","tid":737623,"uid":103914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:38:36.000Z","msg":"第2個失波就是占士米拿的錯<br />\n<br />\n痴撚線占士米拿係比個68號仔陰鳩左喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253259e33e3e0b655a593e0f04f6d7fe711f2ee7","tid":737623,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:39:20.000Z","msg":"又話買當拿隆馬"},{"pid":"f6ed294a0dbf7194171871cf776ef89c34cb69b7","tid":737623,"uid":18669,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:51:55.000Z","msg":"永久性腦震盪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 慘啦"},{"pid":"ad08280dcb6f9a1fd31407a9fd274ca02cfeedab","tid":737623,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6ed294a0dbf7194171871cf776ef89c34cb69b7","tid":737623,"uid":18669,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:51:55.000Z","msg":"永久性腦震盪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 慘啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T04:04:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61810e5d363ddded14513e03044d2dade4320100","tid":737623,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201